versionData.description: Adds a simple force which is controlled by the current wind intensity and direction on Ultra Dynamic Weather

metadata.description: The scale of the velocity added when wind intensity is at its highest,
The velocity in cm/s of the particle.
An exponent used to power the Wind Intensity value from 0 to 1. Higher values will make the center of the range less intense.
The position of the particle. This is its own type for LWC support.
Scales a curl noise sample to add variation to the wind vector
